Hello everyone,

Recently our autos made with pathplanner stopped working in our main branch. It’s still working in a different branch, but there’s no noticeable difference between these two branches that would cause this.

If we try and run an auto in the main branch, you can hear the wheels start to move, and looking on advantage scope the measured states are actively oscillating, but that’s all that happens, no matter what is in the auto.

I tried changing the PID values, but there was no noticeable difference in behavior.

Any and all help would be appreciated!!

This is our main branch: GitHub - AuPiratesFIRST/FRC-2025-Reefscape-Team3291: Team 3291's 2025 Reefscape Competition code

This is the branch that’s seemingly working: GitHub - AuPiratesFIRST/FRC-2025-Reefscape-Team3291 at pathplanner-routes-v1
